# Copy to .env (gitignored). Never commit real values.
#
# --- Presence worker API secret (not SSH) ---
CVC_PRESENCE_SECRET=generate-a-long-random-string

# --- Optional: SSH tunnel password (only if you cannot use ssh keys) ---
# Used by: scripts/cvc_tunnel.sh with `sshpass -e` (reads env var SSHPASS).
# Security: plaintext on disk; anyone with shell access can read .env.
# SSHPASS=your-ssh-login-password

# Optional overrides for cvc_tunnel.sh (defaults match Host cvc_server_tunnel-style setup):
# CVC_SSH_HOST=tunnel.cvc.uab.es
# CVC_SSH_USER=elopezc
# CVC_SSH_PORT=22345
# CVC_TUNNEL_LOCAL_PORT=8080
# CVC_TUNNEL_FORWARD_HOST=158.109.8.17
# CVC_TUNNEL_FORWARD_PORT=80
